events.name: I/O 17 Extended (Night Event)

group.name: GDG Coimbatore : Google Developer Group, Coimbatore

events.description:
About I/O

Google I/O is an annual developer festival held at the outdoor Shoreline Amphitheatre. Each year, Google I/O provides a huge quantity of educational videos, code labs, and blog posts to help developers keep up with the latest in technology.

This event will showcase some of the major announcements from I/O, in-person experiences and insider information from developers who were there, and provide access to hands-on code labs so that developers can try out the new technology!

About I/O Extended

I/O Extended events include a variety of options for developers—from live streaming sessions to local demos, hackathons, code-labs, and more.

In 2016, there were 534 Google I/O Extended events in 100 countries around the world! In the past, GDG Coimbatore has been doing I/O Extended event in Coimbatore from the last 4 years.

We are bringing to you another version of the I/O Extended. Our meetup.com. Come out and join us for a day full of fun and meaningful sessions.

events.name: ML Study Jam - GDG Coimbatore

group.name: GDG Coimbatore : Google Developer Group, Coimbatore

events.description:
It's no more a secret that Artificial intelligence (AI) is transforming the way we live and work, like never before, revolutionizing the world around us. India, home to over a million developers is openly embracing the power of AI across sectors, from health care, education, governance to the economic and cultural well-being of the country.
To empower this journey, Google has joined hands with Niti Ayog to grow the AI ecosystem in India, by training developers, mentoring students and providing research grants to universities across the country. Contributing to this larger idea of building an “AI empowered India”, Google has launched Machine Learning (ML) Study Jam Series from June 1st to end of 2018 with the aim to enable a platform to learn for ML enthusiasts.

ML Study Jams are a series of free, community run, in-person study groups where participants learn, network and build ML solutions to tackle India specific challenges together. The primary goal of Study Jams is to raise the technical proficiency of participants in ML. These participants will leverage the Machine Learning Crash Course and TensorFlow Tutorials developed by Google as the main curriculum to deliver in their study jams.

The detailed agenda of topics we are going to cover:

Day 1 - Dec 21

9:30 AM Registration & GDG Coimbatore Intro By GDG Team
10:00 AM to 10:30 AM Keynote By Pratyusha Simharaja (Video Call)
10:30 AM to 01:00 PM Python and 3rd Party Libraries By Mohamedsipli
02:00 PM to 04:30 PM ML Algorithms By Mohamedsipli

Day 2 - Dec 22

10:00 AM to 01:00 PM Tensorflow and Neural Network By Mohamedsipli
02:00 PM to 04:30 PM Web Scraping and NLP By Mohamedsipli

Day 3 - Dec 23

10:00 AM to 11:00 PM ML for Mobile By Harshit Dwivedi (Video Call)
11:00 PM to 01:00 PM ML for Web By Mohamedsipli
02:00 PM to 04:30 PM Advanced ML and AI By Mohamedsipli.
4.30 Thank you Note.

Speakers:
1. Pratyusha Simharaja - Program Coordinator ML Education, Google. (https://www.linkedin.com/in/pratyusha-simharaju-79aa8128/)
2. Mohamedsipli - MLCC Facilitator, Google. (https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohamedsipli/)
3. Harshit Dwivedi - MLCC Facilitator, Google. (https://www.linkedin.com/in/hadwivedi/)

upcoming.name: IWD WTM Coimbatore Awards 2020

group.name: GDG Coimbatore : Google Developer Group, Coimbatore

upcoming.description:
Drum roll, please 🥁. The most awaited event of the year is finally here and we're going big! WTM Coimbatore presents to you WTM IWD AWARDS 2020 on the theme "Men Behind Women".

Women have become forthcoming leaders and it's due time to celebrate the supportive men in their lives. The countdown begins ladies and gentlemen. Watch out this space for more updates.

An award function for the first time in the history of Google's WTM(Women TechMakers).
On this 2020 IWD (International Women's Day), *Google's WTM Coimbatore* would like to take a minute to wish every woman who is always been a multitasking person, a very happy Women's day.

IWD WTM Awards 2020 is a recognition for all the women who have contributed in any technical field in Coimbatore. For instance, a woman who has started a technology startup or the CEO of a big company in Cbe. But to make it little interesting, we will not be giving the awards to the women directly, instead, the men who have supported the women and encouraged them to come all the way to where they are today will be recognized and awarded. The man behind the woman can be a father, husband or friend. And there it goes 'Men Behind Women'

We welcome everyone.😊

"Men for Women, Women for Men"

Let us create a world of Equality.

Catch us on

FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/wtmcbe/
INSTAGRAM: wtmcoimbatore
Mail ID: [masked]

Thank you so much for your support! :)
